    "r i is the spatial coordinates for spot i.",
    "Archetypal analysis.",
    "Marker genes that represent cell states may be context dependent or unknown.",
    "To address these limitations and improve the characterization of tissue-dependent cell states, we developed a geometric preprocessing step, leveraging archetypal analysis 75, to refine marker genes and identify new cell states.",
    "Archetypal analysis fits a convex polytope to the observed data, finding the prototypes (archetypes) that are most adjacent to the extrema of the data manifold in high dimension."
